<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss house</title><updated>2025-05-19T08:52:13.976449+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>68a78ad53e23f5f1a7ed58cc8005526e</id><title>🆘UNI Residence開價｜中原陳永傑：定價比同區新盤折讓最多3成 料投資者入市佔比達4成</title><updated>2025-05-18T21:54:07+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-18T21:54:07+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572463144"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572463144"&gt;無乜誠意 今時今日低3成係基本&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="62" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_o05.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑表示，沙田新盤UNI Residence 公布首張價單，涉及50伙，折實呎價由13,882元起，整體較同區新晉二手屋苑有約2至3成折讓，入場費410萬元，相信對上車客及投資者均相當吸引，預計投資者入市比例可達約4成。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;他續指，項目位置方便，鄰近6間大學，租賃需求一直持續高企，參考同區租賃市況，預料落成後呎租可達約65元水平， 租金回報可達約4.5厘，租金回報相當吸引，近日市場利好因素增加，關稅戰緩和，拆息口落，加上內地人行降準，整體入市氣氛明顯改善，近日西沙新盤熱賣，連續5次銷售錄得即日沽清，預計UNI Residence 首輪開售亦不例外，昨日單日新盤錄超過400宗成交，創單日15個月新高，市場預期本月可達3000宗一手成交，創14個月新高，本行5月二手成交亦較上月同期錄約3成增長，若發展商持續以克制價錢推盤，整體成交持續暢旺，樓價於本月尋底機會很大。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3951410%2FUNI%2520Residence%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%2583%25B9%25EF%25BD%259C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258E%259F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%2582%2591%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25AF%2594%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E6%258A%2598%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A3%25E6%2588%2590%2520%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%